snippet.title: RBI Chief Urjit Patel Heckled By Congress Workers At Kolkata Airport

localized.description:
On a day Bengal's ruling Trinamool Congress declared that the Central government's currency ban had resulted in nearly a hundred deaths, Urijit Patel, governor of the Reserve Bank of India or RBI, came within an inch of being manhandled at the Kolkata airport by angry Congress workers.
